Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷可是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM系统?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托付给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰哥…约翰哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.20,0:00:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭载于Gundam上的这功能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔上没有相关资料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是预先装载于GN驱动器的黑匣子中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 维塔内机师们的资料也被完全删除了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说伊奥利亚·肖汉博格预测到了我的计划变更
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以神自居的理想主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不甘心再任凭你摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:47.88,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}拉格朗日1 资源卫星群
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭用荚舱 开始与托勒密连接
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾部推进器 收容完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敌人来犯之前要完成整备 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将积存于机体内的高浓度压缩粒子全面解放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一定时间内可得到3倍于常规的马力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有原型太阳炉才被赋予的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM系统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚大叔倒给我们留下了不起的礼物了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 使用了TRANS-AM系统之后 机体性能会大幅下降
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所谓两面刃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那发来的暗号通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 接受托勒密的返舰命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有要件报告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停在地上的拟造太阳炉搭载型MS全部升空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 一架Gundam Throne机体被敌人捕获
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕获?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是国联军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:04:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢夺了Throne的驾驶员是 亚里·阿鲁·沙歇斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚里·阿鲁·沙歇斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那混蛋在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算为非作歹到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是佣兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是补给完成在先 还是国联军来犯在先
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是哪个 战斗都会在拉格朗日1展开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:23.13,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}国联军 弗吉尼亚级大型运输舰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然周到地把预备部件也准备好了 真是有心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗 捕获这架Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顶武特务部队 塞鲁哥·斯米卢诺夫中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到俄罗斯的暴熊亲自来打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法国 第4独立外人骑兵联队加里·比亚吉少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特来参加Gundam讨伐作战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挺想听听看你如何捕获Gundam的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那属于企业机密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离可视战斗宙域还有2000
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 一级战斗戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS部队准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到这时候了 霍华德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到答案了吗 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我们 被伊奥利亚·肖汉博格所托付
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 我就以自己的意志 为根绝战争而战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与Gundam一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我不认为我们能够做到根绝战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们所进行的这些愚蠢行为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是好是坏 都会深刻在人们心中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我认为天行者组织 我们的存在不是有意义的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类只对经历过的事物才能理解其真正的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 捕捉到国联军的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近中的运输舰为UNION的弗吉尼亚级 数量三
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离可视战斗领域还有4200
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 利用资源卫星 后撤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios Virtue 准备防卫战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 于托勒密待机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不至于吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然上了锁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做有点强硬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可不是用嘴说得通的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在上一次战斗中被他所救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 这次就由我来保护他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 固定于线性区
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:07:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 阿雷鲁亚·哈普狄斯姆 开始迎击行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌运输舰上的MS出发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue 提艾利亚·爱德 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌MS 拟造太阳炉搭载型 26架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌MS部队中有Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向所有驾驶员传令 出击的Gundam只有2架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用245阵型应战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包围 歼灭之
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 请期待我的战果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会干掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会干掉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家还真是有干劲的好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先制攻击开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新装备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚣张什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了尾部推进器 机动性上升了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机 不要破坏阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按E计划进行各个击破
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击无效
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 Throne吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉它 獠牙!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来随你们干了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接命中?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验体E57!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·皮瑞斯么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 尾部推进器破损
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与疑似搭乘超兵的MS交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue 正受到敌MS集中攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向Gundam发出后退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥 能听到么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames它…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用GN兵装进行对舰攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是按你的战术来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 陪我一下咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚里·阿鲁·沙歇斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在 少尉!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠落吧 Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头…头痛竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑量子波我给你屏蔽掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷鲁亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀光他们吧 阿雷鲁亚!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T…TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光芒是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新兵器么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大佐~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子残量已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你下手可够狠啊 Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机 急速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN兵装…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯特拉特斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中攻击新来这架
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 现在没功夫一个个瞄咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我弹幕制压吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击开始 攻击开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样开始进入对舰攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 你那身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢你关心了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 TRANS-AM的临界时间已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收场还真难看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios Virtue
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子再装填之前 机体性能低下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破敌MS部队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已进入对舰攻击行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啊 刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌MA接近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用磁轨炮 应战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气端了老家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norfolk击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距到达还有180秒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就结束了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚里·阿鲁·沙歇斯吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是惯用眼被…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KPSA的沙歇斯吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 听库尔吉斯的小鬼说了么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥爱尔兰自杀恐怖袭击的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是佣兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AEU的轨道电梯建设
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中东会反对是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢把无关的人也卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是同类么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行什么战争根绝的恐怖主义者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会接受罪罚的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在此之前要先打倒你!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 地点已确认
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接解除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用TRANS-AM 前往战斗宙域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这制造战争的源头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神气什么 你不也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我和你相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要将这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机接近 敌机接近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里吗 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍华德的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是UNION的 Flag机师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右边看不见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不见!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:17:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损伤严重 损伤严重…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗不能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没死么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是顽固的小强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 把Dynames引导回托勒密号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 我会活着回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳炉 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:18:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了 伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM 的活动极限
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的 躲哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干掉这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把仇报了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不能前进啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不能面对世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活体反应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准射击!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做的话 可是会回不去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不到过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 这之后的明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔活着的未来就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 找到答案了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 GN兵装
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们满意了么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很讨厌的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios Viture仍然健在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现Dynames
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在返回托勒密的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员平安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.97,0:21:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.29,0:21:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人!
